orchestrator_pkg.builders -> task_runner_pkg.task_runner_impl_pkg.WorktreeTaskLogCapture: registers { class: dependency }
orchestrator_pkg.builders -> task_runner_pkg.task_runner_impl_pkg.WorktreeTaskTeardown: registers { class: dependency }
